00:06:12,742 --> 00:06:15,765
And in mid-2013, I was able to really start planning in

110
00:06:15,845 --> 00:06:16,225
earnest.

111
00:06:17,703 --> 00:06:22,126
The first thing I needed to do was work out why I wanted to bring it on to Plague Inc.

112
00:06:22,386 --> 00:06:26,988
There's vast numbers of different reasons, and I know this is the business money track,

113
00:06:27,008 --> 00:06:29,749
so I've got a big list of business reasons to share with you all.

